item.title: The Netherlands 2016
item.description: The first stop on my first trip to the European continent. Some of the European InKAS 2016 Summer Camp participants decided to host a reunion in Amsterdam. Initially it seemed like gathering was going to be mainyl Dutch and a few other Europeans. But my good friends convinced me to not only join, but to also stay in Europe an extra week and explore. Highlights of the trip included riding bikes around the streets of Amsterdam, meandering through the Red-light district, a guided boat tour through the canals of the city and enjoying some quality time with good people.
